{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4bdcd46fec","title":"戚本禹对河南郑州十大总部的讲话","origin":"1967年8月16日河南二七公社赴京汇报代表团编《中央首长关于河南问题的指示及赴京汇报纪要汇编》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1a6e529cc5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"4bdcd46fec"}],"tags":[{"id":"33f01f9c5a","name":"李先念","type":"人物"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3ae36abefb","name":"刘建勋","type":"人物"},{"id":"57434e107b","name":"戚本禹","type":"人物"},{"id":"9a50528209","name":"纪登奎","type":"人物"},{"id":"9e41d5677c","name":"河南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"979308fdfb","type":"title","text":"戚本禹对河南郑州十大总部的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"5fa9f4485f","type":"authors","text":"戚本禹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"47ffe45d54","type":"subtitle","text":"（时间：六月二十八日晚）","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"9eb7a53b11","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：都来了吗？谈一谈你们来了多少人？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"5ec8e40e48","type":"paragraph","text":"秘书讲：十六个人。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"ee7a0c0e66","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：怎么这么多？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"94bc5424d7","type":"paragraph","text":"秘书：那些都是我们的联络员。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"2dccd891dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（新乡老保李玉坤进来送材料）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"9d7f367146","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你是十大总部的？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"b51b95104b","type":"paragraph","text":"李玉坤：我是新乡的。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"048ae554ef","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你不是，你出去。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"28ca4af7b7","type":"paragraph","text":"李玉坤：你讲过以后，我还有事给你谈。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"06c300ee1c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：好，你先回去等！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"038eaf2b81","type":"paragraph","text":"李玉坤：我在门口等你！","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"a9daa0c9eb","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：到你住的那个地方等吧！","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"2772bf6306","type":"paragraph","text":"（李玉坤灰溜溜地走了）","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"bec6ddfea7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对十大总部）你们一次会还没开过吗？","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"db834283e7","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"0de1fdfe99","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：中央开会，请你们来汇报，希望你们好好学习毛主席著作，进行整风，检查自己的错误，由我们的联络员领导你们。你们十大总部什么时候成立的？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"c85e054b5d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：大约是二月底成立的。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"cba527341e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：是不是三月成立的。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"bad01aa08a","type":"paragraph","text":"戚问：军区承认你们是左派组织吗？","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"8eab2e06ab","type":"paragraph","text":"答：军区一直不理我们。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"0331540977","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们成立以后，不斗走资本主义道路的当权派，一直斗群众。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"fcdc008b03","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们根本没有斗群众，大方向是正确的。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"6795e70fff","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚本禹同志发脾气了）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"8a4233c9e5","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：是错误的，二七公社、河造总还承认错误，你们不承认错误？公安公社来了没有？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"21fcc9c3c7","type":"paragraph","text":"公安公社答：我们的大方向是正确的。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"99aadd3d51","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（大发脾气）始终是错误的，你们帮助军区抓人，违反了毛主席亲自批的八条。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"729a416ec9","type":"paragraph","text":"公安公社：看是啥时候？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"948f46fcb0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：啥时候也是错误的，干尽了坏事，没干一点好事（大发脾气）。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"9d051d44cb","type":"paragraph","text":"公安公社：（狡辩说）我们抓人是军区批准的。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"1441440861","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们不要把责任都推给军区，你们的责任跑不了。我就不想接见你们。你们既然来了，希望你们好好学习，彻底检查你们的错误，起来造反。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"976013d4ea","type":"paragraph","text":"公安公社：我们来就带有材料，你听我把情况汇报一下。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"30fdd42edc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（生气地说）我不听你的汇报，我的态度就是粗暴，对你们就是不客气。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"fd92043228","type":"paragraph","text":"工交公社石油公司一代表发言：我们运动一开始就打倒刘建勋、打倒纪登奎。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"23a98ca833","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（生气地说）你们打倒刘建勋就是大方向的错误，纪登奎也打不倒。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"905f5753fa","type":"paragraph","text":"工人总部：我们是群众组织，刘建勋在河南犯了滔天罪行，我们群众喊打倒他，你们中央批准不批准在你们。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"19db9cb9d2","type":"paragraph","text":"工人总部（放肆地说）：我们为什么不可以喊“打倒刘建勋”，喊打倒就是大方向的错误吗？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"389b26d820","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们喊打倒是你们喊的，喊打倒就是错误的。其余别的你们喊打倒没有？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"4f2c12ef22","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我们喊打倒刘建勋！打倒文敏生！打倒纪登奎！打倒王黎之！省市委我们哪一个没有轰呀！","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"4a477140df","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（很恼火地问公安公社代表）你是党员不是？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"ab6254d12c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"46ad9301f9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：什么时候入党的？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"cf885f19b7","type":"paragraph","text":"答：1960年！","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"d072481a0e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：在公安厅搞什么工作？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"396b29fa6b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：公安公社夺权后，我是勤务员。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"f33c2f9a3c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（生气地指着十大总部讲）你们都是保守组织。公安公社干尽了坏事，抓了多少人！逮捕了多少革命群众！你们违反了毛主席亲手批准的八条命令。抓了多少人啊！","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"88789c07b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一个财贸总部的人说：我们抓的是打人凶手，是坏人。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"a022b6db0e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：抓了一万多人都是坏人吗？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"3e52c6f041","type":"paragraph","text":"公安公社（放肆地反问道）到底抓了多少人？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"4567940788","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（非常生气地讲）你们亲手抓的，还来问我！","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"af95f5765a","type":"paragraph","text":"老保反问：就有一万多人？","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"ce3051fbec","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：军区都承认了，你们还不承认？","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"67f11a9f99","type":"paragraph","text":"财贸总部：请首长派人调查？","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"e357d6533c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（非常生气地说）：我说的话都没有调查吗？我们已经派了好多人去调查了。我不是首长，我不是首长，我不是首长！","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"ab7b006243","type":"paragraph","text":"财贸总部：首长！你不知道我们在河南的情况，根本抬不起头来！","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"2dd910ff84","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们不是抬不起头来，是压倒一切！","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"c7c9db359d","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我要向首长汇报。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"0445cb52f9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（生气地讲）：我不听！你要讲，给我们联络员去讲。联络员领导你们学习，希望你们检查错误，起来造反。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"f75d108a21","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部（插嘴说）：我们的大方向始终是正确的，根本没有错误。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"a5b73789d4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我给二七公社提的缺点，他们都听进去了，你们根本听不进去。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"f2a98a527a","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军代表：我是铁军的。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"7675bd8d79","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（生气地说） 铁军不要讲了，你们的战绩我都知道。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"7c95569946","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军（插嘴说）：首长，听我给你汇报！……","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"efcc400f96","type":"paragraph","text":"戚（打断他的话说）：我不是首长，我是个小组成员。不听你的汇报，（生气地站起来说）我说的不对，你们可以贴我一百张大字报，可以炮轰我，我还是要坚持。你们贴“十大总部必胜！”我说“不胜！”","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"24e1cbf4ea","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：首长，那不是我们贴的。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"da5eed5eca","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：怎么不是你们贴的！","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"3d5f39c0cf","type":"paragraph","text":"铁路老保站起来说：我是铁路工人……","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"cc944beb9c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚（打断他的话说）：你不是铁路工人，你是代表！","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"407b45bc05","type":"paragraph","text":"铁路代表：二七公社是内保、外保！","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"1bc57fee88","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：看保的是什么人？看谁保的对！","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"c78e851929","type":"paragraph","text":"工交公社石油公司的人说：我们是起来造反最早的一个单位，给李先念写过报告。李先念亲自批了我们的报告！","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"a777f60f90","type":"paragraph","text":"戚（发脾气了）：李先念批准你们的报告，我不知道。你们先起来造反，可能；但是还可以变坏！","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"76b6f45341","type":"paragraph","text":"工交代表：（发脾气，质问戚本禹同志）你有什么根据说我们是保守组织？","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"150552edb5","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（一拍沙发站起来，非常生气地说）我看，你们就是保守组织。你的这个态度就是保守组织。不讲了！ 我今天来，就是宣布联络员领导你们学习，认真检查错误。下一次听你们汇报。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"6193a72e58","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我们欢迎，我们就是要向中央汇报的。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"695a6dd9db","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：（又站起来说）我们要汇报。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"3fb7f99687","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（很生气地说）我不听！我要回去了，有什么事向我们联络员汇报，群众大部分是好的，总部的头头，比如公安公社到底是什么人，我怀疑！","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"5fe9fb8b45","type":"paragraph","text":"市委代表：（站起来说）我们是最早起来造市委反的。","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"cdcdf18b91","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我看不见得。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"226a8f6871","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚本禹同志站起来，离开了会场）","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"baee03c82e","type":"paragraph","text":"（十大总部代表们个个垂头丧气）","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"cf8daa0269","type":"paragraph","text":"1967年6月28日晚  首都动态组","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"0700ffbe6b","type":"appellation","text":"","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"535a704777","type":"subtitle","text":"版本二：","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"2dd41b6458","type":"subtitle","text":"戚本禹1967年6月28日接见河南十大总部代表讲话(摘要)","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"416e017076","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：“公安公社”来没有？","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"f416c2570f","type":"paragraph","text":"公：来了，我们的大方向始终是正确的。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"28092d47c4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：(生气)始终是错误的！你们帮助军区抓人，违反主席亲自批的军委八条，干尽坏事，没办一点好事！","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"b622656961","type":"paragraph","text":"公：我们抓人都是军区批准的。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"cbab3df025","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们把责任都推给军区，你们的责任跑不了，我就不想接见你们，你们既然来了，希望你们好好学习毛主席著作，彻底检查错误，起来造反。","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"d716e5d532","type":"paragraph","text":"公：我带来有材料，听我们汇报。","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"bd1d13f591","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我不听你们汇报！！我的态度就是粗暴，对你们就是不客气。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"3206f3bcea","type":"paragraph","text":"石：(石油公司)我们开始就打倒刘建勋，打倒纪登奎。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"710345ff26","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们打倒刘建勋就是方向错误！！纪登奎也打不倒！！","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"db10d3a713","type":"paragraph","text":"石：我们是群众，刘建勋在河南五年犯了滔天罪行，我们喊打倒刘建勋，你们中央批准不批准在你们，我们为什么不能喊打倒呢？打倒刘建勋就是大方向错误！？","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"5e004d8291","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：喊打倒刘建勋就是在大方向错误！！！你们喊打倒是你们喊的，喊打倒就是错误的！其他你们喊打倒没有？！","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"6b779a43df","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们都是保守组织！“公安公社”干尽了坏事！！抓了好多人，逮捕了好多革命群众！！你们违反了毛主席亲自批准的军委八条，抓了那么多人！！","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"049e65e35e","type":"paragraph","text":"女：(有一女的)我们抓的打人凶手是坏的。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"dce2f3e173","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：抓了一万多都是坏的？！军区都承认了，你们还不承认？","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"39fb929bdc","type":"paragraph","text":"女：首长派人调查！","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"826ea24cfd","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我们不是首长，我说的没有调查吗？我们已经派好多人调查了！","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"19a8c82373","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：首长听我汇报。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"1457ed90a9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我不是首长！！我不听你们汇报，我说的不对，你们可以贴一百张大字报，可以炮轰我，我还要坚持，你们要贴大字报“十大总部必胜”，你们不胜。","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"77f07124f0","type":"paragraph","text":"有人在嘟囔：“二七公社”内保，外保。","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"82ebeb3586","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：看保的什么人，看谁保的对。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"1cc1b45680","type":"paragraph","text":"石：你有啥根据(指戚)宣布我们为保守组织！！(大声吵)","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"a30fc63aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：(站起来)我看你就是保守组织，我看你就是保守组织(大声)，看你的态度就是保守组织，不讲了，我今天宣布，联络员领导你们学习，认真检查错误。下次听你们的汇报。","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"},{"id":"0215997b1d","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：周良霄顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》，2009。","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec"}],"page":{"id":"6d2a9d177d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4bdcd46fec","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}